<p>I'll also change the message to "Database Exception".</p>
<p>Refresh! Cool: it still catches that exception. But check this out: go back into
<code>PdoShipStorage</code> and - before the query - throw a different exception: there's one
called <code>InvalidArgumentException</code>:</p>
